parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results.

>  You must specify the token that is obtained from the previous query as the value of NextToken.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Valid values: 0 to 100. Default value: 20.

parameters.name: ServiceName
parameters.description: The Alibaba Cloud service. For more information about the Alibaba Cloud services supported by ActionTrail, see [Services that work with ActionTrail](~~28829~~).
